@startuml level1_single_agent
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFF9C4

title **Level 1 — Single Agent (Baseline)**

|Client|
start
:Submit business question;

|#E3F2FD|Generic Agent|
:Receive client question;
:Research the market;
:Analyze financials;
:Identify risks;
:Synthesize findings;
:Write consulting report;
:Return report to client;

|Client|
:Receive report;
note right
  **No evaluation**
  **No role separation**
  **No specialization**
  ----
  Single model handles
  everything end-to-end
end note
stop

@enduml
